{"tid":698598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【9個月死112人】墨西哥再有政治人物遇刺　國會候選人辯論會場外中槍斃命","createTime":"2018-06-11T23:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T02:38:55.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08be34a9640e7ffcc4784de012a003a7df12613f","tid":698598,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T23:55:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【9個月死112人】墨西哥再有政治人物遇刺　國會候選人辯論會場外中槍斃命</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180611/s00005/4d221eb1b35015654eb8f054adba5d24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180611%2Fs00005%2F4d221eb1b35015654eb8f054adba5d24.jpg&h=e925e5cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥國會選舉下月1日舉行，一名候選人上周剛在選舉辯論中表示，一旦當選將「正面面對」罪案，惟一步出會場即中槍身亡。他是選戰去年9月展開以來，第112名被殺的政治人物。<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥國會科阿韋拉州（Coahuila）候選人佩龍（Fernando Puron），上周五（8日）在他曾任市長的彼德拉斯內格拉斯市（Piedras Negras），參與選舉辯論後離開會場。他應一名途人要求停下拍照，幾秒後有另一名男子現身，向其頭部開槍，佩龍當場死亡。拍得案發經過的閉路電視黑白片段，未能清楚顯示兇徒樣貌，警方暫未拘捕任何涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥總統的培尼亞（Enrique Pe&ntilde;a Nieto）2012年12月上任以來，國內一直有聲音批評他無力應對毒品罪案。佩龍遇害前，在選舉辯論上曾被問到如何改善阿韋拉州的公共安全，回應稱「要正面面對罪案，不能害怕」，不料他剛離開辯論會場即被殺害。<br />\n<br />\n佩龍一名黨友正競逐連任彼德拉斯內格拉斯市長，在是次謀殺案發生後，已宣布無限期暫停選舉活動。<br />\n<br />\n自選戰去年9月展開以來，連同佩龍在內，墨西哥已有112名從政者被殺，其中最少39人來自佩龍隸屬的革命制度黨（Institutional Revolutionary Party，PRI）。墨西哥全國32個州中，22個州曾發生政治人物遇害案件。<br />\n<br />\n（CNN）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180611/s00005/1528708336431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180611%2Fs00005%2F1528708336431&d=4SVUfAwZUVteQo%2F0z4mZtUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=53721ae9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180611%2Fs00005%2F1528708336431&h=74c18285\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180611/s00005/1528708336431</a>"},{"pid":"7c8362eebbf50f71d98ad2780a5f4d3ebd40103a","tid":698598,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"支那如果也是這樣，就好了"},{"pid":"3fc771badaba909be57b9a2832912f0ad5913faf","tid":698598,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c8362eebbf50f71d98ad2780a5f4d3ebd40103a","tid":698598,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"支那如果也是這樣，就好了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"支那係冇人出黎選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed38aa2b554dbcdd716121d07be1676eb9f65733","tid":698598,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc771badaba909be57b9a2832912f0ad5913faf","tid":698598,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c8362eebbf50f71d98ad2780a5f4d3ebd40103a","tid":698598,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"支那如果也是這樣，就好了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"支那係冇人出黎選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:46:44.000Z","msg":"頭半句啫"},{"pid":"38baf2a6dc811ec9476925379cd7d5dd014580a3","tid":698598,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"咁不如搵毒販去選好過喇"}]}